OL,3,C'You don't want to take up a bed' -
OL,4,Chow the NHS is caring for patients at
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FThe NHS in Somerset is caring for
OL,8,Fpatients at home to reduce pressure on
OL,9,Fhospitals during the winter period.
OL,11,FDr Phil Raines, respiratory medicine
OL,12,Fconsultant at the Somerset NHS Trust,
OL,13,Fsaid that the winter pressure on
OL,14,Fregion's hospitals is, "incredibly
OL,15,Fstressful for everybody, from the
OL,16,Fmanagers working at the top to the
OL,17,Fpeople working on the shop floor.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
