OL,3,C'You don't want to take up a bed' -
OL,4,Chow the NHS is caring for patients at
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"So when they're in their homes, they
OL,8,Fdo their normal things, they keep
OL,9,Ftheir strength up, and they recover
OL,10,Fmore quickly."
OL,12,FMike Stone is a patient at Taunton
OL,13,FHospital who was diagnosed with COPD
OL,14,Fin 2009.
OL,16,FNow, instead of being treated in
OL,17,Fhospital, Mike's nurse Vicky comes to
OL,18,Fcare for him in his own home. Nurses
OL,19,Fat Taunton Hospital can even monitor
OL,20,FMike's observations remotely.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
