OL,3,C'You don't want to take up a bed' -
OL,4,Chow the NHS is caring for patients at
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FMike says: "You just do not want to go
OL,8,Finto hospital and take up a bed -
OL,9,Fthere's so many nurses involved.
OL,10,FWhereas like this it's just one nurse
OL,11,Fthat comes out and does all the jobs.
OL,13,F"It works out pretty good really and
OL,14,Fsaves me blocking that bed in
OL,15,Fhospital."
OL,17,FVicky - Mike's nurse - says it is
OL,18,F"fulfilling to be able to give this
OL,19,Fsort of care at home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
