OL,3,C'You don't want to take up a bed' -
OL,4,Chow the NHS is caring for patients at
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F'Bed blocking' is one of the biggest
OL,8,Fcontributors to NHS pressures. It's
OL,9,Funderstandably made even worse in the
OL,10,Fwinter when there is greater demand
OL,11,Ffor treatment for respiratory
OL,12,Fconditions.
OL,14,FIt's caused by several factors, one of
OL,15,Fthe big ones being the crisis in adult
OL,16,Fsocial care.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
