OL,3,C'You don't want to take up a bed' -
OL,4,Chow the NHS is caring for patients at
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FEarlier this year he promised to
OL,8,F"finally grasp the nettle on social
OL,9,Fcare reform" but, in the same breath,
OL,10,Fadmitted it "would take time".
OL,12,FThe end goal for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,13,Fgovernment is to set up a new National
OL,14,FCare Service, but with a commission on
OL,15,Fsocial care reform not due to publish
OL,16,Fits recommendations until 2028, there
OL,17,Fis a while to wait yet.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
