OL,3,C'You don't want to take up a bed' -
OL,4,Chow the NHS is caring for patients at
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FThe PM says his government has taken
OL,8,F"immediate action" to fix the social
OL,9,Fcare crisis - like boosting the carers
OL,10,Fallowance - and is working on "longer-
OL,11,Fterm reform".
OL,13,FThe government is aiming to change
OL,14,Fsome things in the meantime, though.
OL,16,FLabour has promised more funding for
OL,17,Felderly and disabled people to make
OL,18,Fimprovements to their homes and avoid
OL,19,Fgoing to social care settings, as well
OL,20,Fas funding for care workers to provide
OL,21,Fhealth checks for patients at home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
